{
  "stem": "25912.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I remember the date because when I arrived there there were Canadian nuns.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was the order of St.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Felix.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they were celebrating St.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Valentine's Day, the first time I've ever heard of St.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Valentine's.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So that identifies the date when I arrived there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I don't know when I left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "After that I moved around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Also before I went to the convent I move around staying with various people having been brought up by a patriot father, I knew that there was an underground and a resistance movement.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Mrs.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] daughter was very active in the girl guides.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I was desperate to join.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Everybody was a bit wary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I would be hiding on two counts.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But I was allowed to join a unit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And that was a great boost to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And one of my friends in the guides was Hania Nowodworska, whose father had been the president of the Lawyers' Association and as such was arrested by the Germans when they occupied Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He was then released but his health had suffered enormously and he died shortly afterwards.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Her mother was a very active member and one of the leaders of an association that was looking at the political prisoners in Warsaw's jails and did wonderful work passing messages and ensuring that the prisoners knew what they were supposed to say, coordinating what was said by different people at great risk to themselves.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "At one stage I stayed with her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And somehow in conversation we were sitting together burning law books in a fireplace to keep warm.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I let slip names of lawyers in the family, one of my grandfather's sister had married a leading Polish lawyer.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
